      <title>加拿大部长称阿尔伯塔省阻碍了加拿大的关税应对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/canada-s-tariff-response-hurt-by-alberta-pushback-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大自然资源部长表示，阿尔伯塔省省长丹尼尔·史密斯 (Danielle Smith) 承诺反对联邦政府削减或征收对美原油出口税的计划，这将削弱加拿大抵制美国可能征收关税的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/canada-s-tariff-response-hurt-by-alberta-pushback-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 16:17:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
